text: Arhopaloscelis bifasciatus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Kraatz in 1879. It is known from China, Japan, Russia, and Siberia.BioLib.cz - Arhopaloscelis bifasciatus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1879
